08:58.496 --> 09:00.581
[washing machine whirring]

09:05.002 --> 09:06.754
[knocking]

09:10.049 --> 09:12.176
[knocking continues]

09:12.260 --> 09:16.305
Ugh, yeah, yeah, hold on.

09:16.389 --> 09:18.516
Hey, uh, I'm sorry to knock
so loud, Lucas,

09:18.599 --> 09:19.684
but I didn't know
if you were in or not.

09:21.560 --> 09:25.189
Yeah, I'm-- I'm in. Sleeping.

09:25.273 --> 09:27.650
-Oh, yeah, I'm sorry--
I'm sorry to wake you.
-Nah.

09:27.733 --> 09:31.362
But I just thought
that we would get
the day started.

09:32.947 --> 09:34.782
Um...

09:35.616 --> 09:37.368
Do you remember me at all, kid?

09:37.952 --> 09:41.539
No, sorry.

09:41.622 --> 09:44.333
Okay, I met you a few times
when you would come to visit

09:44.417 --> 09:46.335
your father
when you were little.

09:46.419 --> 09:48.337
I guess you were too young.

09:48.421 --> 09:50.172
Yeah.

09:50.256 --> 09:52.008
You still got
the same baby face.

09:53.968 --> 09:54.844
-Yeah.
-[chuckles]

09:54.927 --> 09:57.513
Well, okay.
You know, enough reminiscing.

09:57.596 --> 10:00.266
I just thought that,
you know, I would take you out,

10:00.349 --> 10:02.852
we'd make the rounds
and introduce you
to all the tenants.

10:02.935 --> 10:05.146
-Yeah.
-I'm the groundskeeper
slash superintendent.

10:05.229 --> 10:07.565
Well, I kind of work better
alone, so...

10:08.607 --> 10:12.028
-You work--
-Listen, I appreciate
this whole "father figure,

10:12.111 --> 10:17.700
help me out" thing,
but I'm good, thanks.

10:17.783 --> 10:19.160
-You're good?
-Yeah.

10:19.243 --> 10:22.079
Okay.
You know what?

10:22.163 --> 10:23.622
I'll be around if you need me.

10:25.166 --> 10:30.379
-See ya, kid.
-Oh, um, hey, what's the deal
with me selling the place?

10:33.424 --> 10:34.216
-In terms of what?
-Selling the place.

10:34.300 --> 10:35.760
I want to sell the place.

10:36.844 --> 10:38.721
Well...

10:39.764 --> 10:42.141
first, you have to go through
all your father's stuff.

10:42.224 --> 10:43.768
Make sense of it all.

10:43.851 --> 10:46.062
Is there like a 30-day notice
I gotta give everyone?

10:46.145 --> 10:48.189
All the tenants?

10:48.272 --> 10:49.607
So they can go away?

10:50.316 --> 10:52.651
Yeah, your pops,
he said you would be like this.

10:52.735 --> 10:56.155
Haven't seen him in ten years.
Did he tell you that?

11:00.701 --> 11:03.412
-I'll see you around, Baby Face.
-Hey, don't call me that.

11:03.496 --> 11:05.414
That's-- that's not my nickname.

11:06.248 --> 11:08.292
[man]
See you around, Baby Face.

11:11.504 --> 11:14.799
[man speaking Spanish
over PA]

11:17.051 --> 11:20.221
[Spanish continues]

11:30.981 --> 11:32.817
[light music playing]

11:34.568 --> 11:35.778
[Lucas] Yo, what up?

11:37.613 --> 11:42.701
-What up, bro?
-Um, is, uh, Kieffer here?

11:42.785 --> 11:44.662
Yeah, if you're looking
for Guala Boy

11:44.745 --> 11:47.498
to sign something for you,
it's not gonna be a good day.

11:47.581 --> 11:50.501
Yo, what the fuck?

11:50.584 --> 11:51.502
Lucas!

11:51.585 --> 11:53.754
[laughs]
Damn!

11:53.838 --> 11:56.632
-It's so fucking
good to see you.
