12:21.240 --> 12:24.326
My first pro deck.

12:24.410 --> 12:26.328
-[Lucas] Ooh...
-Eh, what you think?

12:26.412 --> 12:28.372
-[both laughing]
-That's awesome.

12:28.456 --> 12:31.125
