the graphics and everything
on that.

12:31.208 --> 12:34.253
-Yeah, I can tell.
-[both laughing]

12:34.336 --> 12:35.921
Eh, you want one?
They gave me a bunch.

12:37.631 --> 12:39.175
Yo, yo, yo.

12:39.258 --> 12:40.634
You're the guy from Reno Rats.

12:40.718 --> 12:42.970
