12:43.053 --> 12:45.681
-Hey, Lucas! Varela!
-Varela! Yo!

12:45.764 --> 12:48.684
Look,<i> Reno Rats Two,</i>
like, we still have that
on the VHS,

12:48.767 --> 12:51.854
-Put that on the VCR.
