12:57.860 --> 13:00.404
Damn, dude,
I barely recognized you.

13:01.197 --> 13:03.073
What do you do?
You still skate?

13:06.118 --> 13:08.787
Nah, I don't really do
any of that shit anymore.

13:11.040 --> 13:13.876
[rolling skate wheels]

13:26.305 --> 13:28.432
Mm, fuck!

13:28.516 --> 13:29.642
[huffs]

13:44.240 --> 13:46.575
