13:59.213 --> 14:00.631
Don't worry about it.

14:02.508 --> 14:03.759
Sorry, I didn't mean to...

14:04.718 --> 14:07.680
I was just--
I was just being a dick.

14:09.723 --> 14:11.058
Teach me a trick.

14:12.017 --> 14:14.311
Yeah, that's gonna be
a no from me, dawg.

14:14.395 --> 14:15.938
You don't think I can skate
'cause I'm a girl?

14:16.021 --> 14:18.649
-Is that what it is?
-No.

14:18.732 --> 14:20.859
