17:02.271 --> 17:03.021
It still has its quirks.

17:05.149 --> 17:08.527
Do you know that James Dean
lived up on the third floor?

17:08.610 --> 17:10.237
For real?

17:10.320 --> 17:12.030
No, I'm just fucking with ya.

17:14.950 --> 17:16.618
Fuck you.

17:16.702 --> 17:18.162
It's okay to ask for help...

17:20.247 --> 17:21.373
sometimes.

17:25.711 --> 17:29.423
[door opens, closes]

17:29.506 --> 17:31.759
-[distant traffic hums]
-[birds chirping]

17:38.390 --> 17:42.269
-Yo, what the fuck?
-Whoa, Jesus, I thought
there was nobody here.

17:42.352 --> 17:42.811
-Hey, man, hey.
-Hey! Hey!

17:42.895 --> 17:44.646
Hey, wait! Whoa, whoa.

17:44.730 --> 17:46.231
Hey. Hey, Lucas, it's me.

17:46.315 --> 17:48.150
-Who the fuck are you?
-It's me. It's me.

17:48.233 --> 17:49.485
Who?

17:50.944 --> 17:51.653
