He's like, "Good thing
I brought my Heelys,"

20:42.074 --> 20:43.867
and he just like slid away.

20:44.910 --> 20:46.495
Nothing, that's what happened.

20:47.579 --> 20:50.707
Yo, remember
she was dating Kev's dad
back in high school for a bit?

20:50.791 --> 20:52.459
What the--?
No, bro.

20:52.542 --> 20:53.877
